&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://Amarantos-Arrebol.github.io/p/linux-exercises/Linux%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A.assets/image-20251101203629680.png&#34;
	width=&#34;529&#34;
